    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，StudentDB推送数据到ClassroomService的收件箱。那LMS门户这边呢？Education_LMS_Portal需要参与吗？",
