    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：StudentDB推送到Inbox，LMS门户通过agent-bus连到StudentDB，然后RepoScan从ClassroomService引出。接下来数据怎么流转？",
      "elements_involved": [
